    cookies are used, a cookie consent banner is not legally required under the Privacy and Electronic
    Communications Regulations 2003 (PECR).
  </p>
  <p>
    Cloudflare may use a technical cookie (__cf_bm) for bot detection and DDoS protection. This cookie
